SeriesDesc: Countries with National Human Rights Institutions and no status with the Paris Principles, C status (1 = YES; 0 = NO)
Source: Source: The Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights (OHCHR) in collaboration with Global Alliance of National Human Rights Institutions (GANHRI).
Footnotes: Name of National Human Rights Institution: Commission fédérale pour les questions féminines (CFQF) (Mar 2009); Federal Commission against Racism (FCR) .
